      "idx": 0,
      "start_ms": 0,
      "end_ms": 4700,
      "text": "아직 상황 파악이 잘 안 되나 본데 난 너희 부녀를 위해서 호의를",
      "target_text": "It seems you still haven't grasped the situation, but I'm doing this as a favor for you and your daughter.",
      "speaker_id": "A",
      "audio_path": "speech/0001_0_4700.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0001_0_4700.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start_ms": 4700,
      "end_ms": 9220,
      "text": "베푸는 거야 지금 당장 전화한 통화로 애초에 없었던 일로 만들 수도",
      "target_text": "With just a phone call right now, I could make this all go away as if it never happened.",
      "speaker_id": "A",
      "audio_path": "speech/0002_4700_9220.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0002_4700_9220.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start_ms": 9220,
      "end_ms": 9580,
      "text": "있고",
      "target_text": ".",
      "speaker_id": "A",
      "audio_path": "speech/0003_9220_9580.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0003_9220_9580.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start_ms": 9580,
      "end_ms": 15480,
      "text": "니놈 딸을 다시는 못 보게 만들 수도 있다고 여기까지 오는 동안",
      "target_text": "I could make it so you never see your daughter again, and during this time, I've been thinking about what you should do.",
      "speaker_id": "A",
      "audio_path": "speech/0004_9580_15480.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0004_9580_15480.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start_ms": 16920,
      "end_ms": 22420,
      "text": "넌 어떻게 해야 할지 고민했어 이제 확실해졌다",
      "target_text": "Now it's clear.",
      "speaker_id": "B",
      "audio_path": "speech/0005_16920_22420.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0005_16920_22420.wav"
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start_ms": 23080,
      "end_ms": 24520,
      "text": "민지를 위해서",
      "target_text": "For Minji,",
      "speaker_id": "B",
      "audio_path": "speech/0006_23080_24520.wav",
      "audio_url": "/v1/local/step12/14ef1d62c3da48c7b37560ea3417d1b6/speech/0006_23080_24520.wav"
    },
